#: ../../source/applying_special_fx.rst:15
msgid "Using the FX Schematic"
msgstr "Uso del Diagrama de efectos"

#: ../../source/applying_special_fx.rst:16
msgid ""
"In the FX schematic all columns/layers are displayed as nodes having an output "
"port connected to the Xsheet node: this means that their content is part of the "
"scene and is rendered as it is."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/applying_special_fx.rst:18
msgid ""
"When effects are added, they are displayed as nodes as well, with ports to "
"create links that let you set the way the FX affect the scene contents."
